{"tid":1442630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府迴避「721 官警黑元朗恐襲」","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:16:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T00:46:28.000Z","uid":158613,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"56f98961ffe1a4321e7dbd7bfe5b5fb04d9d11ca","tid":1442630,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:16:45.000Z","msg":"721 官警黑元朗恐襲<br />\n<br />\n726 張建宗向市民道歉 及 警察屌張建宗<br />\n<br />\n811 張建宗對警隊的專業表現和克制，予以充分肯定和全力支持。<br />\n他指，<span style=\"color: red;\">反送中 已停止，近日的暴力行為，明顯偏離最初原則。 (但對 721 官警黑元朗恐襲 隻字不提)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家完全忘記了<span style=\"color: red;\">721 官警黑元朗恐襲 係激起最大民憤嘅原因，大量中立撚都醒哂，呢個核彈政府係無得拆的</span>，所以今個星期開始拉返大家去Focus 反送中 。<br />\n<br />\n我明白5大訴求 缺一不可，但呢家要先用 「721 官警黑元朗恐襲」 打破缺口。"},{"pid":"2d4c5f860eca54f4a7b7ca0847229b53c8962cdc","tid":1442630,"uid":18354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:20:55.000Z","msg":"【求置頂】我係811港島東集會搞手，請大家冇野做就黎維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(冇人講)今日去深水埗!!!!唔好上淘寶！推爆我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19</a><br />\n<br />\n[求今日置頂] 811港島東要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[811] 深水埗 港島東 機場和你飛final call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cb46b174bb4c23b551f76ac64e73031cc97be830","tid":1442630,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:22:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f6674db596cc46d516a3fda2f8ae9bb8575e5f2","tid":1442630,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjQ517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjQ517.jpg&h=8be1ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【求置頂】我係811港島東集會搞手，請大家冇野做就黎維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n(冇人講)今日去深水埗!!!!唔好上淘寶！推爆我！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442131/page/19</a><br />\n<br />\n[求今日置頂] 811港島東要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442282/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[811] 深水埗 港島東 機場和你飛final call<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1442525/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e91a7edc95836b6e45b13f037d57fb9205e9c722","tid":1442630,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:24:09.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"a36643eeea6bc9866a04c26a9de79d9644da626d","tid":1442630,"uid":20070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMJqUur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMJqUur.jpg&h=36fb98e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbU1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=e686ffc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">44,418</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 10:56）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本識 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bde119481a093edcd5fed4c27d0b969eae6136b5","tid":1442630,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:25:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657a6a32f2504f3a7c50a5a5d6c23f98eafe4f5a","tid":1442630,"uid":290176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c